@zegrib For files that are above 720p you should use "Splash lite player"

Vlc player and others have problemes with files above 720p

Splash lite player is a free player that is free

@zegrib

Start splash lite player, right click, select settings, select video, click the box up to the left which says use hardware acceleration.

ALSO everytime you play a video start splash lite player with that video then close splash lite wait 30 seconds and start it again with the video
